# Python BTK Akademi

The repo shows my advanced python and project related training examples that I have done during the course.



## Installation

clone the relevant project. (You will receive a link from our repo here)

` git clone https://github.com/kaleliguray/python_btkakademi.git `



## Usage

After cloning the project, open it in Visual Studio Code or other ide.

For Linux:

```
cd python_btkadademi
code .
```
